â€œWhite Urkle is the perfect sleeper. The strain profile says almost nothing about effects but buckle up boys and girls. It smells amazing, the effect is heady, while also packing a crazy, powerfully heavy body high. Be careful and go slow this stuff can sneak up on you.â€

â€œSis in law flowed me a heavy gram just now and dayum...not reading leaflys guide yet, I'd say the high is similar to GSC, maybe sunset sherbet...I'm functional and locked at the same time. back pain gone. future's rapping/mumbling makes much sense to me now. I could go for a jog, but why? esp when it's 105Â° at 2130...let's play some Diablo 3 instead.â€

â€œWhite Urkle was very relaxing. A strong head buzz hit me hard and fast, followed by an all over relaxed feeling. This strain diminished anxiety and pain for me. I felt mentally clear, even as a nice couch lock settled in. The high lasted about 30 minutes.â€
â€œis a great smooth organic bud, I feel like I can inhale all the buds vapour instead of coughing which I am accustomed to. Smooth piney taste that makes this a great choice.â€

â€œI'm still a relatively new smoker, and suffer from panic disorder, but White Urkle has definitely been a favorite so far. Its calming effects are amazing. â€œHaving tried a few urkle crosses, this is one of the best. Dense purple glistening nugs. The high is strong and pure indica. Relaxing and sedative while uplifting and euphoric. Great all around body high. Flavor is some sweet berry with earthy spicy musky undertones. Got it at Serra in Eugene. Will definitely get it againâ€

â€œI absolutely love this strain. One can definitely feel the indica inside of this glorious hybrid. White Urkle is a great strain to have when you have nothing to do and just want to sit around with some friends on the back porch and some good food.â€

â€œMajor Pain relief... my body buzzes after one hit. And Iâ€™m a chronic pain patient with a collapsing pelvis ( not fun.)

â€œSuper tasty. Especially the concentrate. Mellow yet heavy head high.â€

â€œgot this as a 1 gram preroll accidentally. ordered white widow. â€œA mellow skunky smell.  Alright/ tame taste and smoke. But what always matters the most of course is the Effecf: & Holy moly! Clear but happy mind and BEST of all it makes my spine like pasta! Euphoria Delight baby!  Toke more than a nice hit or two and ...â€

â€œWow do I love this flower. Awesome potency, tastes great and the high is A1. Very relaxing yet uplifting. I've got a permanent smile when puffing on this lady. Grab this strain next time your out, you will be very satisfied.â€

â€œKind of made me paranoid. But smells and tastes amazing!â€

â€œDensely packed bright green buds covered in crystals.  Flowers almost look like they have been rolled in kief.  Effects are chill and relaxed, but not to the point of a couch lock.  Vapour is smooth with hints of citrus and peat.  Very earthy and rich smoke.â€
â€œGreat strain for evening relaxation. Very pungent and so delicious! Looks beautiful. Thanks, Cannabliss - Burnside!â€
â€œGreat Hybrid that gives you instant relaxation and feelings of happiness, the flavor is sweet with a bit of earthy citrus after taste.â€

â€œUsed this strain as a wake and bake bud, but that is a huge mistake cause you won't get up and be active for about 2 hours after you finish smoking. The purple urkel indica is expressed as a thick body buzz with a tingling behind the ribcage, and the white is expressed as a roaring cerebral high sativa, I definitely am impressed with this cross of 2 potent strains!â€
â€œTightly packed buds with crystals and hairs everywhere.  Chill but very uplifting.â€
â€œgreat relaxing High. I love the way it looks. HD pictures of the nugs look amazing.â€
â€œthis snow cover bud is amazing and mellow. Very chill. I would recommend for depression it's very up lifting.â€

â€œPicked his strain up for the daytime burn and I have to say it's quite a treat to smoke! Very flavorful and grew out some thick dense buds leaning on the indica side of things. As for the flavor it's got fruit notes and the high settles into the front of your head. You need a good sharp stone style grinder for this type of flower quite dense. Overall I would buy this againâ€

â€œVery relaxing yet non-drowsy high accompanied by easily amused happiness. Very talkative and heady but with a stoned feeling such that I wouldn't use this for going out or in social settings. 

The indica side is not noticeable by doesn't hit with the hard withdrawal into my head, sleepiness, and couch lock I experience with some hybrids like PGSC. Instead I found myself understanding things in minute detail, very en...â€

â€œWhite Urrrrrrkel is a very heavy/heady strain with a unique nose and taste, too. I wasnt a huge fan of the taste--like plat-oh and pears maybe? Hard to describe, but overall it was a great experience......â€
â€œIt is a relaxing body high. great after working out or work. a blunt of this knocked out my best friend. the best high with a vaporizer.!â€

â€œThis stuff is amazing. My BIL got me an eighth for pain and insomnia and I slept for 13 hours last night uninterrupted. Best nights sleep of my life. â€œReally good, taste so good, and not a lot of coughing involved either, so really really good.  Did I mention that it was good?â€
